        construct coupon object and get id, title, start date, end date, amount, type, message, price and image
        Parameters:
        id - id of coupon - generated automatically from DB
        title - name of coupon
        startDate - the date the coupon started
        endDate - the date the coupon expire
        amount - the amount of coupon
        type - coupon type
        message - describe the coupon
        price - coupon price
        image - image of the item
